Uchujin installed.

Next steps:
  1. bundle exec rails db:migrate
  2. Edit config/initializers/uchujin.rb (auth + notifications)
  3. Visit /uchujin in your app

Deploy hooks (optional):
  POST /uchujin/api/deployments  with Authorization: Bearer $UCHUJIN_DEPLOY_TOKEN
  Body: { "sha": "...", "environment": "production", "user": "kamal" }

Check-ins (cron heartbeats):
  POST /uchujin/api/check_ins/:name/ping

Uptime monitoring: schedule Uchujin::UptimeCheckJob with URLs via recurring SolidQueue/cron.
